量的 _InactiveRpcError 异常\n\n3. **影响范围**：由于 recommendationservice 不可用，导致所有依赖它的前端服务在获取产品推荐时失败，进而触发了上下文取消错误。\n\n4. **时间关联**：错误集中在 17:11-17:20 期间，与故障时间窗口高度吻合。\n\n**建议**：需要进一步检查 recommendationservice 的资源使用情况、网络连接状态以及服务健康状态。", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on the metric data analysis, I can identify the root cause of the fault. The data shows significant performance degradation across multiple services, with the frontend service experiencing the most severe impact.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend service\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe response time degradation with rrt and rrt_max metrics showing massive increases (600x+), combined with elevated error_ratio and client_error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend pods show rrt increased from ~12.5s to ~9.5M (600x+), rrt_max from 196k to 60M (300x+), error_ratio from 0% to 15-16%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"High error_ratio and client_error_ratio across all pods during fault period\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice pods show error_ratio and client_error_ratio increased from 0% to 60%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Elevated error_ratio and client_error_ratio indicating service degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1 and productcatalogservice-2 show error_ratio increased from 0% to 30-32%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Moderate error_ratio and client_error_ratio increases affecting transaction processing\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice pods show error_ratio increased from 0% to 14-15%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的trace数据分析，我现在可以识别故障根因。让我分析这些数据：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->recommendationservice\", \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"推荐服务响应时间从正常的3.8秒激增至4.77亿秒（约5.5天），延迟倍数超过120,000倍，这是最严重的延迟异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"推荐服务调用产品目录服务的ListProducts操作从2.8秒激增至4.35亿秒，说明推荐服务内部依赖产品目录服务时出现严重延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端调用推荐服务的ListRecommendations操作出现大量context canceled错误和HTTP 500错误，表明推荐服务不可用导致前端请求失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析要点：**\n\n1. **根因定位**：`recommendationservice` 是故障的源头，其响应时间异常激增（从3.8秒到4.77亿秒），远超正常值。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：\n   - `recommendationservice` 内部调用 `productcatalogservice` 时出现严重延迟\n   - 这导致 `frontend` 调用 `recommendationservice` 时超时，产生大量context canceled和HTTP 500错误\n\n3. **错误类型**：\n   - 状态码14（UNAVAILABLE）和\"Connection timed out\"表明服务连接超时\n   - 状态码1（context canceled）表明上游服务主动取消请求\n   - HTTP 500错误表明服务端内部错误\n\n4. **网络vs服务**：从调用链分析，时间主要消耗在服务处理而非网络传输，说明是服务本身性能问题。"}
